Available Tools: create_volume | attach_volume | detach_volume | snapshot_volume | list_volumes
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "volume_id": "string", "instance_id": "string", "size_gb": number }
Response Schema: { "volume_id": "string", "size_gb": number, "state": "string", "attached_to": "string" }
---
Question: Enumerate all storage blocks in the eu-west-2 zone to find unused capacity for new deployments.
Call: { "func_call": "list_volumes", "volume_id": "", "instance_id": "", "size_gb": 0 }
Response: { "volume_id": "vol-9z8y7x6w5v4u3t2s1", "size_gb": 250, "state": "available", "attached_to": "" }

Question: Generate a recovery point for the analytics volume vol-analytics-raw before running the ETL pipeline.
Call: { "func_call": "snapshot_volume", "volume_id": "vol-analytics-raw", "instance_id": "", "size_gb": 0 }
Response: { "volume_id": "vol-analytics-raw", "size_gb": 1200, "state": "snapshotting", "attached_to": "i-etl-worker-05" }

